    to convert that to `Xe_Core` count by dividing the `EU` count by
    `8`(this number was taken from the [oneAPI Optimization
    Guide](https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/docs/oneapi/optimization-guide-gpu/2025-0/intel-xe-gpu-architecture.html)).
    
